`doc-default` is an existing test file. I chose it because it had a single section whereas `sct-section-props` has like 3 so I thought that might muddy the waters. But I suppose it doesn't really matter. We'll just always use `sections[0]` for these tests that aren't specifically testing multi-section functionality.

